Repeat: p3, slip next 4 stitches to dpn and hold in front, drop next stitch off left needle; slip the 3 purl stitches from dpn back tothe left needle, then with point of dpn pick up dropped stitch and place it on left needle after the 3 purl stitches; then k1, p3 from left needle; then k1-b from dpn; p3
